title: ISic001749. I.Sicily inscription 001749
body:
Facsimile Images

((ivy-leaf)) Γ(άϊος) ((·)) Βέτουος
((ivy-leaf)) Δημήτριος
χρηστὸς καὶ ((·)) ἂ- ((ivy-leaf))
μεμπτος ἒζη-
5σε ((·)) ἒτη ((ivy-leaf)) ξ´ μῆ(νας) ((ivy-leaf)) η´

Apparatus criticus

Text of Orsi 1893

English translation

Gaios Betouos Demetrios, worthy and blameless, lived 60 years, 8 months.
